TECHNICAL LAWS — ZERO TOLERANCE
━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━
FILE      → Single index.html. All CSS in <style>. All JS in
            <script>. Fonts via Google Fonts <link> only.
            No external JS libraries. No CDN scripts.
            Pure vanilla HTML5 + CSS3 + ES6+.

CSS       → CSS custom properties for all colors/spacing.
            Unique class names (prefix: hx- ) to prevent
            collision. No inline styles except JS-animated
            values. Mobile-first with min-width breakpoints.
            768px (tablet) + 1024px (desktop) + 1440px (wide).

JS        → One DOMContentLoaded wrapper. Sections clearly
            commented. requestAnimationFrame for all animation
            loops. IntersectionObserver for scroll triggers.
            Passive event listeners. Debounce resize handler.
            All canvas elements with aria-hidden="true".

HTML      → Semantic: header/nav/main/section/article/footer.
            Every section has id="" for anchor navigation.
            aria-labels on all interactive elements.
            Skip-to-content link first in body.
            Meta: charset, viewport, title, description,
            og:title, og:description, og:type, canonical.

PERF      → 0 layout shifts. Hardware-accelerated only.
            will-change: transform on animated elements.
            Image-free (use CSS/SVG/Canvas only).
            Target: loads < 500KB total, renders < 1s.

